ED_Title: Promotion and protection of human rights
ED_DecisionText: At its 53rd plenary meeting, on 17 December 2024, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Third Committee.  (Footnote: A/79/458.)
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/79/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
